{"word":"ἀξιόμαχος","slug":"ἀξιόμαχος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀξιόμαχος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μάχομαι'><el>μάχομαι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a match for</i> another <i>in battle</i> or <i>war</i>, <el>τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; <el>πρός τινα</el> <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>: <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <i>sufficient in strength</i> or <i>number</i> to do a thing, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b> <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-χως</el>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}